ðŸš€ AI Automation using n8n â€“ LinkedIn Post Generator

This project demonstrates how workflow automation and AI can be combined to build a real-world application using n8n.

The system generates professional LinkedIn posts based on a given topic by leveraging API-based workflows, webhooks, and AI models.

ðŸ“Œ Project Overview

The goal of this project is to understand and implement:

Workflow automation concepts

Webhook-based requestâ€“response systems

AI-powered content generation

Backend-to-frontend integration

The automation is triggered via an API call, processes the input using AI, and returns a generated LinkedIn post.

ðŸ§  How It Works

A POST request is sent with a topic (e.g., AI in Healthcare).

The n8n Webhook triggers the workflow.

An AI model generates a LinkedIn-style post.

The workflow sends the response back as JSON.

The result can be tested via Thunder Client or integrated with a UI/backend.





